{"type":"question","id":10637,"title":"西南石油大学给留学生配冰箱厨房，本科却没热水，学生：屡见不鲜 怎么看待？","uid":8988,"topics":[402],"contents":"原帖地址：<a href=\"http://baijiahao.baidu.com/s?id=1649456753434030227&amp;wfr=spider&amp;for=pc\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">http://baijiahao.baidu.com/s?id=1649456753434030227&amp;wfr=spider&amp;for=pc</a><br>\n<br>\n<br>\n<br>\n<a href=\"http://pics4.baidu.com/feed/1c950a7b02087bf4c190b9de3acbe22911dfcfac.jpeg?token=b6fac39d844379df3e36213f8cbce984&amp;s=EA9A7689CE0378CC728158000300F090\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"http://pics4.baidu.com/feed/1c950a7b02087bf4c190b9de3acbe22911dfcfac.jpeg?token=b6fac39d844379df3e36213f8cbce984&amp;s=EA9A7689CE0378CC728158000300F090\" alt=\"http://pics4.baidu.com/feed/1c950a7b02087bf4c190b9de3acbe22911dfcfac.jpeg?token=b6fac39d844379df3e36213f8cbce984&amp;s=EA9A7689CE0378CC728158000300F090\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><br>\n近日，西南石油大学给留学生宿舍配冰箱，配厨房等，而本科生宿舍连热水都没有，引起了该校学生及网友的热议及质疑。<br>\n<br>\n西南石油大学建了栋新宿舍，目前只有留学生和部分研究生入住。今日被学生拍到有冰箱被搬进该栋宿舍。据该校同学表示，这种类似的现象已经屡见不鲜。<br>\n<br>\n<a href=\"http://pics0.baidu.com/feed/3ac79f3df8dcd100a833f906ba93f215b9122f03.jpeg?token=25a3d49fe84eb83d3bf6c57dcdb20ecf&amp;s=B9B461950CC252C85C34804C0300C0F2\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"http://pics0.baidu.com/feed/3ac79f3df8dcd100a833f906ba93f215b9122f03.jpeg?token=25a3d49fe84eb83d3bf6c57dcdb20ecf&amp;s=B9B461950CC252C85C34804C0300C0F2\" alt=\"http://pics0.baidu.com/feed/3ac79f3df8dcd100a833f906ba93f215b9122f03.jpeg?token=25a3d49fe84eb83d3bf6c57dcdb20ecf&amp;s=B9B461950CC252C85C34804C0300C0F2\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><br>\n对于此事，学校给的解释却很难让人信服。<br>\n<br>\n<a href=\"http://pics4.baidu.com/feed/fd039245d688d43fd6a0a587b506671e0ef43b53.jpeg?token=b63a360b01418e15efb8620ae12c058a&amp;s=1090ED3303EEDCEA10E5F5CB0100E0B3\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"http://pics4.baidu.com/feed/fd039245d688d43fd6a0a587b506671e0ef43b53.jpeg?token=b63a360b01418e15efb8620ae12c058a&amp;s=1090ED3303EEDCEA10E5F5CB0100E0B3\" alt=\"http://pics4.baidu.com/feed/fd039245d688d43fd6a0a587b506671e0ef43b53.jpeg?token=b63a360b01418e15efb8620ae12c058a&amp;s=1090ED3303EEDCEA10E5F5CB0100E0B3\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><br>\n<a href=\"http://pics6.baidu.com/feed/37d12f2eb9389b50e82bb5a04d2d50d8e6116e0e.jpeg?token=f5c128f1435107c4f59b9762bf289619&amp;s=01186433515E65CC4E7DA8DB0000D0B2\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"http://pics6.baidu.com/feed/37d12f2eb9389b50e82bb5a04d2d50d8e6116e0e.jpeg?token=f5c128f1435107c4f59b9762bf289619&amp;s=01186433515E65CC4E7DA8DB0000D0B2\" alt=\"http://pics6.baidu.com/feed/37d12f2eb9389b50e82bb5a04d2d50d8e6116e0e.jpeg?token=f5c128f1435107c4f59b9762bf289619&amp;s=01186433515E65CC4E7DA8DB0000D0B2\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><br>\n同时，学校也告知学校的学生不要参与、转发和评论此事，甚至是打电话让删除消息。<br>\n<br>\n<a href=\"http://pics4.baidu.com/feed/f2deb48f8c5494ee16810b69e5ed55fb99257e39.jpeg?token=3e035b377dabd205ecf49c05f5901d61&amp;s=CCE232679CB1AC511CBDD59E0100C081\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"http://pics4.baidu.com/feed/f2deb48f8c5494ee16810b69e5ed55fb99257e39.jpeg?token=3e035b377dabd205ecf49c05f5901d61&amp;s=CCE232679CB1AC511CBDD59E0100C081\" alt=\"http://pics4.baidu.com/feed/f2deb48f8c5494ee16810b69e5ed55fb99257e39.jpeg?token=3e035b377dabd205ecf49c05f5901d61&amp;s=CCE232679CB1AC511CBDD59E0100C081\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><br>\n<a href=\"http://pics5.baidu.com/feed/38dbb6fd5266d016f1e5c30f5f33610235fa3533.jpeg?token=5fac37305f4b493cdcd297805131eb42&amp;s=4018E033CF205C01087514DB000090B3\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"http://pics5.baidu.com/feed/38dbb6fd5266d016f1e5c30f5f33610235fa3533.jpeg?token=5fac37305f4b493cdcd297805131eb42&amp;s=4018E033CF205C01087514DB000090B3\" alt=\"http://pics5.baidu.com/feed/38dbb6fd5266d016f1e5c30f5f33610235fa3533.jpeg?token=5fac37305f4b493cdcd297805131eb42&amp;s=4018E033CF205C01087514DB000090B3\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><br>\n<a href=\"http://pics4.baidu.com/feed/962bd40735fae6cdbce13ecec8abba2143a70fe2.jpeg?token=c5ff71c0cc299c39d1d4b92ecfe3c7cf&amp;s=C888E01394A84D0142F111D6010010B2\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"http://pics4.baidu.com/feed/962bd40735fae6cdbce13ecec8abba2143a70fe2.jpeg?token=c5ff71c0cc299c39d1d4b92ecfe3c7cf&amp;s=C888E01394A84D0142F111D6010010B2\" alt=\"http://pics4.baidu.com/feed/962bd40735fae6cdbce13ecec8abba2143a70fe2.jpeg?token=c5ff71c0cc299c39d1d4b92ecfe3c7cf&amp;s=C888E01394A84D0142F111D6010010B2\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><br>\n<a href=\"http://pics2.baidu.com/feed/f7246b600c338744fbeba48996176cfcd72aa033.jpeg?token=52c0e1daa62b8012430817fff6849835&amp;s=A840ED17055A55CA48C490DB0300C030\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"http://pics2.baidu.com/feed/f7246b600c338744fbeba48996176cfcd72aa033.jpeg?token=52c0e1daa62b8012430817fff6849835&amp;s=A840ED17055A55CA48C490DB0300C030\" alt=\"http://pics2.baidu.com/feed/f7246b600c338744fbeba48996176cfcd72aa033.jpeg?token=52c0e1daa62b8012430817fff6849835&amp;s=A840ED17055A55CA48C490DB0300C030\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><br>\n本校学生表示，现在本科生宿舍都没热水，只有极少部分本科生能被抽签抽到有热水的研究生及留学生宿舍中，同样是上学，条件差的太多。<br>\n<br>\n由于网上对于此事的持续热议和质疑，学校给出了说明。<br>\n<br>\n<a href=\"http://pics3.baidu.com/feed/72f082025aafa40ffd414569637cb64a79f01999.jpeg?token=e16c4d0cdded08086639477e0624d0f3&amp;s=B112C07E93BEC46D143694830200A089\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"http://pics3.baidu.com/feed/72f082025aafa40ffd414569637cb64a79f01999.jpeg?token=e16c4d0cdded08086639477e0624d0f3&amp;s=B112C07E93BEC46D143694830200A089\" alt=\"http://pics3.baidu.com/feed/72f082025aafa40ffd414569637cb64a79f01999.jpeg?token=e16c4d0cdded08086639477e0624d0f3&amp;s=B112C07E93BEC46D143694830200A089\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a>","date":"2019-11-07","agreeCount":7,"discussionCount":0}